---
title: "User Data Deletion - BrightGift"
description: "Learn how to request deletion of your personal data from BrightGift."
---

<Layout title="User Data Deletion - BrightGift">
	<main class="min-h-screen bg-[#FFF9F3]">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#1C2E4A] mb-8 text-center">User Data Deletion</h1>
			
			<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 space-y-6">
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#1C2E4A] mb-4">Your Right to Data Deletion</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						At BrightGift, we respect your privacy and your right to control your personal information. You have the right to request deletion of your personal data from our systems at any time.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#1C2E4A] mb-4">What Data We Store</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
						We may store the following types of information:
					</p>
					<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1 ml-4">
						<li>Gift recommendation queries and preferences</li>
						<li>Recipient information you provide</li>
						<li>Budget and occasion details</li>
						<li>Website usage analytics</li>
						<li>Communication history with our support team</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#1C2E4A] mb-4">How to Request Data Deletion</h2>
					<div class="space-y-4">
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-[#1C2E4A] mb-2">Email Request</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
								Send an email to <strong>privacy@bright-gift.com</strong> with the subject line "Data Deletion Request" and include:
							</p>
							<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1 ml-4 mt-2">
								<li>Your name and email address</li>
								<li>Specific data you want deleted (or "all data")</li>
								<li>Reason for deletion (optional)</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-[#1C2E4A] mb-2">Contact Form</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
								Use our contact form on the website to submit your deletion request. We'll respond within 30 days to confirm receipt and provide an estimated timeline for completion.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#1C2E4A] mb-4">Deletion Process</h2>
					<div class="space-y-4">
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-[#1C2E4A] mb-2">Verification</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
								We will verify your identity before processing the deletion request to ensure the security of your data.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-[#1C2E4A] mb-2">Processing Time</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
								We will process your deletion request within 30 days of receipt. You will receive confirmation once the deletion is complete.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-[#1C2E4A] mb-2">Backup Data</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
								Some data may be retained in backup systems for a limited period as required by law or for legitimate business purposes.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#1C2E4A] mb-4">What Happens After Deletion</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
						After your data is deleted:
					</p>
					<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1 ml-4">
						<li>You will no longer receive personalized gift recommendations</li>
						<li>Your account preferences will be reset</li>
						<li>You may need to provide information again if you use our service in the future</li>
						<li>We will retain minimal information required for legal compliance</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#1C2E4A] mb-4">Exceptions to Deletion</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						We may retain certain information if required by law, for legitimate business purposes, or to protect against fraud. This includes information necessary for:
					</p>
					<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1 ml-4 mt-4">
						<li>Legal compliance and regulatory requirements</li>
						<li>Fraud prevention and security</li>
						<li>Financial record keeping</li>
						<li>Dispute resolution</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#1C2E4A] mb-4">Third-Party Data</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						If you've used our service to make purchases through affiliate links, those third-party retailers may retain your information according to their own privacy policies. You may need to contact them directly to request data deletion.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#1C2E4A] mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						For questions about data deletion or to submit a request:
					</p>
					<div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
						<p class="text-gray-700">
							<strong>Email:</strong> privacy@bright-gift.com<br>
							<strong>Subject:</strong> Data Deletion Request<br>
							<strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 30 days
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="border-t pt-6">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 text-center">
						Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout> 